Third District.

In re estate of Mary Margaret Thrush. Petitions of Verna V. Edwards and Imo E. Sackett, appellants, v. Edith Lane, executrix of the estate of Mary Margaret Thrush, deceased, appellee.Gen. Nos. 8,089 and 8,094.Opinion filed November 21, 1927.Rehearing denied January 4, 1928.Costigan & Wollrab, for appellants. C. M. Peirce, for appellee. Mr. Justice Niehaus

delivered the opinion of the court.
